title: Area Dick’s stores will have extended hours should Mets clinch Wednesday
text:
MORE Pending a Mets clinching win Wednesday night in the National League Championship Series, DICK’S Sporting Goods at the Freehold Raceway Mall and Brick 70 Plaza will have extended store hours immediately following the game and early Thursday morning (6 a.m.) to make sure fans get their hands on championship gear.
